snippet.title: The Dreamer Must Die - Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
'The Dreamer Must Die' is an RPG shooter where you're the only hope for a fading dream world. Advance the story through multiple routes, find new equipment, and improve your character within the MIND menu to ensure your survival.
You can get it on Steam in Early Access here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2116590/The_Dreamer_Must_Die/
